id: pm-u43m
title: Linked test sandbox cleanup can fail with ENOTEMPTY
description: pm test --run can report failure after linked commands pass because linked-test sandbox cleanup removes /tmp/pm-linked-test-* without retries. The failure was reproduced twice as ENOTEMPTY on the schema directory while validating pm-changelog integration.
type: Issue
status: closed
priority: 1
tags[3]: cleanup,linked-test,tests
created_at: "2026-05-23T20:44:49.461Z"
updated_at: "2026-05-23T20:50:32.434Z"
author: codex-pm-changelog
parent: pm-7811
severity: medium
resolution: "Linked-test sandbox cleanup now retries recursive removal, matching other temp cleanup paths."
expected_result: "pm test --run exits 0 when linked commands pass, even if the OS briefly keeps sandbox directories busy."
actual_result: pm test pm-7811 --run and pm test pm-u43m --run both passed after reinstalling the patched CLI; focused test-command unit suite passed 40 tests.
component: linked-test
comments[1]{created_at,author,text}:
  "2026-05-23T20:50:19.678Z",codex-pm-changelog,"Evidence: patched linked-test sandbox cleanup to use fs.rm maxRetries/retryDelay. Reproduced previous ENOTEMPTY before reinstalling patched CLI, then reran pm test for pm-7811 and pm-u43m successfully after npm install -g .; focused node scripts/run-tests.mjs test -- tests/unit/test-command.spec.ts passed 40 tests."
